 ############################
 WINDOWS CONTROL
 ############################

 
 for horizontal window creating
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------
 | :sp									|
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------
 | :split								|
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------
 | Ctrl-W n								|
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------

 You also can use for open the file with filename "filename"
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------
 | :sp filename								|
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------
 

 for vertical window creating
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------
 | :vsp									|
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------
 | :vsplit								|
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------

 for vertial empty window creating
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------
 | :vne									|
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------

 